<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Saint Xavier University awards academic credit in more than 25 subjects to qualified students for Advanced Placement Exams offered through the College Board. Students should contact an advisor in the Academic Advising and Testing Center at advising@sxu.edu or at 773-298-3011 to determine how AP credit will be applied to specific academic programs.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://catalog.sxu.edu/Undergraduate/ADM/advanced.html" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
